* 1984年获[[艾爾弗·斯隆基金會|阿尔弗雷德·P·斯隆基金会]]奖学金。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Alfred P. Sloan Foundation - Past Fellows|url=https://sloan.org/past-fellows|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Sloan Research Fellowships|archive-date=2018-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314000756/https://sloan.org/past-fellows|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
