* 1986年获卡米尔·德雷福斯（Camille Dreyfus）教师-学者奖。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Camille Dreyfus Teacher-Scholar Awards Program|url=https://www.dreyfus.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/TC.all_.2019.pdf|accessdate=2019-12-02|archive-date=2019-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830185519/https://www.dreyfus.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/TC.all_.2019.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 2005年获洛林国家理工大学的Honoris Causa博士。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Professor awarded honorary degree by French University|url=https://www.iowastatedaily.com/news/article_0ba48bc5-52fe-5c0c-b77a-abde62081f0f.html|accessdate=2019-12-02|author=Brian Oltman|work=iowastatedaily}}</ref> 
* 2008年被选为Iota Sigma Pi名誉会员。<ref>{{Cite web|title=2008 Iota Sigma Pi Honorary Member Award|url=https://www.iotasigmapi.info/awards/professionalawards.html#nhm|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Iota Sigma Pi|archive-date=2019-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190417083301/http://www.iotasigmapi.info/awards/professionalawards.html#nhm|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Ames Laboratory's Pat Thiel Receives Chemistry Honor|url=https://www.ameslab.gov/news/news-releases/ames-laboratorys-pat-thiel-receives-chemistry-honor|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Ames Laboratory|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150804131420/https://www.ameslab.gov/news/news-releases/ames-laboratorys-pat-thiel-receives-chemistry-honor|archivedate=2015-08-04}}</ref> 
* 2010年，因其对表面化学的进步作出的杰出贡献，获亚瑟逊·亚当森奖（Arthur W. Adamson Award）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Arthur W. Adamson Award for Distinguished Service in the Advancement of Surface Chemistry|url=https://pubsapp.acs.org/cen/email/html/8803awards8.html|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Chemical & Engineering News}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Thiel Selected for ACS Adamson Award for Surface Chemistry|url=https://www.ameslab.gov/node/8357|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Ames Laboratory|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150805024712/https://www.ameslab.gov/node/8357|archivedate=2015-08-05}}</ref> 
* 2010年，因其“对复杂金属合金的表面结构和动力学的开创性贡献，包括准晶体以及金属薄膜中纳米结构的动力学受限的生长和弛豫”，获{{le|材料物理学领域大卫·埃德勒演讲奖|David Adler Lectureship Award in the Field of Materials Physics}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=David Adler Lectureship Award in the Field of Materials Physics|url=https://www.aps.org/programs/honors/prizes/adler.cfm|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=American Physical Society|archive-date=2020-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027034416/https://www.aps.org/programs/honors/prizes/adler.cfm|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=2010 David Adler Lectureship Award in the Field of Materials Physics Recipient|url=https://www.aps.org/programs/honors/prizes/prizerecipient.cfm?last_nm=Thiel&first_nm=Patricia&year=2010|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=American Physical Society|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529185746/https://www.aps.org/programs/honors/prizes/prizerecipient.cfm?last_nm=Thiel&first_nm=Patricia&year=2010|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 2010年因其“对金属准晶体表面性质的研究，以及致力于金属纳米团簇和薄膜在金属表面上形成和重排的途径”，当选[[美國科學促進會|美國科學促進會]]会士。<ref>{{Cite web|title=AAAS honors Iowa State, Ames Lab researchers for distinguished science|url=https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2011/jan/AAASfellows|accessdate=2020-08-22|archive-date=2019-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621062444/https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2011/jan/AAASfellows|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 2011年当选John D. Corbett化学教授。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Pat Thiel Named to Corbett Professorship|url=https://www.ameslab.gov/node/9080|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Ames Laboratory|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150804042039/https://www.ameslab.gov/node/9080|archivedate=2015-08-04}}</ref> 
* 2012年因其“对理解准晶体表面的结构，反应性和摩擦学，以及理解金属纳米结构和金属薄膜的生长和稳定性方面的开创性贡献”，当选{{le|材料研究学会|Materials Research Society}}会士。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Materials Research Society Announces 2012 MRS Fellows|url=https://www.advancedsciencenews.com/materials-research-society-announces-2012-mrs-fellows/|accessdate=2020-03-16|author=Dave Flanagan|work=Advanced Science News|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118145256/https://www.advancedsciencenews.com/materials-research-society-announces-2012-mrs-fellows/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=2012 MRS Fellows|url=https://www.mrs.org/mrs-fellows-2012|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=Materials Research Society|archive-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708150508/https://www.mrs.org/mrs-fellows-2012|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 2014年被评为[[物理评论|物理评论]]系列期刊的优秀审稿人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Outstanding Referees Program|url=https://journals.aps.org/OutstandingReferees|accessdate=2019-12-02|work=American Physical Society|archive-date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012061456/http://publish.aps.org/OutstandingReferees|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
* 2014年因其“对理解准晶体表面以及薄膜成核和生长的开创性贡献”获Medard W. Welch奖。<ref name="AVSinterview"/>
* 2019年当选[[美国文理科学院|美国文理科学院]]院士。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Patricia Thiel of Iowa State, Ames Laboratory elected to American Academy of Arts and Sciences|url=https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2019/04/16/patthiel|accessdate=2019-12-02|date=April 16, 2019|work=Iowa State University of Science and Technology|archive-date=2020-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006230527/https://www.news.iastate.edu/news/2019/04/16/patthiel|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 个人生活 ==
1988年，帕·蒂尔与澳洲出生的物理学家James W. Evans结婚，两人共育有两个女儿。<ref name="AVSinterview"/>

去世前的帕·蒂尔曾经罹患[[乳腺癌|乳腺癌]]，而[[乳房摄影术|乳房摄影术]]却未能及时诊断出她的癌症（该情况大约占10%）。<ref name="obituaries">{{cite web |title=Patricia A. Thiel Obituary - Visitation & Funeral Information |url=https://www.adamssoderstrum.com/obituaries/Patricia-A-Thiel?obId=18336909#/obituaryInfo |website=www.adamssoderstrum.com |accessdate=2020-09-15 |archive-date=2020-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200915194541/https://www.adamssoderstrum.com/obituaries/Patricia-A-Thiel?obId=18336909#/obituaryInfo |dead-url=no }}</ref>2020年9月7日，67岁的帕·蒂尔因晚期乳腺癌去世。

